io.hekate.spring.boot.rpc

Annotation Type InjectRpcClient


  • @Autowired
 @Qualifier
 @Documented
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value={METHOD,FIELD,PARAMETER,ANNOTATION_TYPE})
public @interface InjectRpcClient
    Provides support for RPC clients autowiring.

    This annotation can be placed on any autowire-capable elements (fields, properties, parameters, etc) of application beans in order to inject an instance of RPC client proxy (see RpcService.clientFor(Class)) into that element.

    See Also:
    HekateRpcServiceConfigurer, RpcService.clientFor(Class)

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      String tag
      Specifies the RPC tag that should be used for this client (see RpcClientConfig.setTag(String)).

    • Element Detail

      • tag

        public abstract String tag
        Specifies the RPC tag that should be used for this client (see RpcClientConfig.setTag(String)).
        Returns:
        RPC tag.
        Default:
        ""
